data.description: Welcome to this stunning home located within the highly sought-after Deer Creek School District. This captivating home boasts three generously sized bedrooms, two bathrooms, and two inviting living areas. Upon entry, you will love the inviting feel of the spacious living room, featuring 10-foot ceilings, and it open to the kitchen and dining area. The kitchen showcases stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a designer tile backsplash, and a fantastic island with breakfast bar. Beyond the living room, a second living area awaits, complete with a vaulted ceiling and a gas fireplace, creating the perfect flexible space for any of your home office or secondary living needs. Just off the kitchen is the perfect office nook features a built-in desk and additional storage! The primary suite is spacious, featuring a spa-like bath with whirlpool tub, double vanity, and a separate shower. Within the walk-in closet, a concealed safe room awaits. The secondary bedrooms are equally spacious, offering ample closet space as well. This property rests on a generous 0.25-acre lot, situated in one of Deer Creek School's most desirable neighborhoods. The Grove features 2 pools, playgrounds, 2 fitness centers, basketball court, fishing ponds and much more with convenient turnpike & highway access. Welcome Home!
